    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Transfer your <strong>BBQ pulled pork</strong> and any juices to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Cover with <strong>tin foil</strong> and put the dish in the oven for an initial 30 min</p>",
