    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>apple[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(skin on) in half and discard the core</p><p>Grate <strong>half </strong>the <strong>apple[s]</strong>, then cut the <strong>remaining apple[s]</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-7-1688141124159-x200.jpg",
