            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 30 min, remove the dish with the pulled pork from the oven and discard the <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Pull the <strong>BBQ pulled pork</strong> apart using two forks and mix everything through the juices</p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 5-6 min further or until the sauce has been absorbed and the pork has started to crisp</p>",
