    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill your <strong>toasted brioche bun</strong> with the <strong>apple sauce</strong>, <strong>smoky stuffing</strong>, <strong>BBQ pulled pork</strong>, <strong>apple slaw</strong> and your <strong>crispy onions</strong> – this are your <strong>BBQ pulled pork hog roast sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>BBQ pulled pork hog roast sandwich </strong>with the <strong>roast waxy potatoes</strong> and any <strong>remaining slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
